                                                                                              SI-14           NON-PERSISTENCE
                                                                                                              ASSESSMENT OBJECTIVE:
                                                                                                              Determine if:

                                                                                                              SI-14_ODP[01]         non-persistent system components and services to be implemented are deﬁned;

