                                                                                                                                    session of use; <SI-14_ODP[03] frequency>};

                                                                                                              SI-14_ODP[03]         the frequency at which to terminate non-persistent components and services that
                                                                                                                                    are iniated in a known state is deﬁned (if selected);

                                                                                                              SI-14[01]             non-persistent <SI-14_ODP[01] system components and services> that are iniated
                                                                                                                                    in a known state are implemented;
